      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with all major systems functioning properly. While there may be minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the interior is clean and the exterior has been well-preserved. It offers a comfortable ride and is ready for many more miles on the road.",
