      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine has a significant oil leak and struggles to stay running, while the transmission experiences harsh shifting. The exterior shows its age with faded paint, several noticeable dents, and bubbling rust on the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic features, including the radio and power windows, are currently non-functional. It will require a comprehensive mechanical overhaul and bodywork to be safely returned to the road.",
