    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without that heavy new-car price tag, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how gorgeous it is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
