    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, an engine renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 11.5:1 compression ratio. This specimen is mechanically flawless; the critical dual-VANOS system has been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has undergone structural reinforcement to eliminate common chassis fatigue. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential, providing surgical precision in torque distribution. The exterior retains its factory paint depth and clarity, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters are devoid of typical ingress wear, and the tactile feedback of the original bushings remains firm and communicative. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car for the enthusiast who demands uncompromising mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Garage kept. Single owner. Zero accidents. Full service history. Interior pristine. Mechanical inspection passed.",
