    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior finish retains its deep, glass-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and every tactile switch operates with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with only genuine parts used. From the spotless engine bay to the pristine undercarriage, this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it left the dealership. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
